Companion Normal Mode
    Events
        Unit - A unit Starts the effect of an ability
    Conditions
        (Ability being cast) Equal to Normal Mode 
    Actions
        Sound - Play GoodJob <gen>
        -------- Turn off other Modes --------
        Trigger - Turn off Companion Passive Mode Active <gen>
        Trigger - Turn off Companion Aggressive Mode Active <gen>
        -------- Start current mode --------
        Game - Display to (All players) the text: Companions: Normal ...
        Trigger - Turn on Companion Normal Mode Active <gen>
        Trigger - Run Companion Normal Mode Active <gen> (checking conditions)
        -------- ====================================================== --------
        -------- Force Stop units --------
        Unit Group - Pick every unit in Companion_Group and do (Actions)
            Loop - Actions
                If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                    If - Conditions
                        ((Picked unit) is alive) Equal to True
                    Then - Actions
                        Unit - Order (Picked unit) to Stop.
                    Else - Actions
        -------- ====================================================== --------
